src:
Dawn reveals MV teaser for 'Money'
01 Nov 2019, 16:40 by sl278
Dawn has revealed his first MV teaser or his solo debut track "Money".
The cinematic teaser definitely shows that a lot of work has been put into the making of the MV, and fans are excited to finally see Dawn make his solo debut under P-Nation.
Check out the teaser above!
